[% META
   title = "Coming Soon"
   description = "This section is under development"
   roles = "public"
   TemplateType = "Application"
   category = "ENCY"
   page_version = "0.01"
   last_updated = "2026-04-04"
%]
[% PageVersion = 'ENCY/ComingSoon.tt,v 0.01 2026/04/04' %]
[% IF c.session.debug_mode == 1 %][% PageVersion %][% END %]

<p><a href="[% c.uri_for('/ENCY') %]">&larr; Back to Encyclopedia</a></p>

<h1>[% entity_name | html %]</h1>

<div class="alert alert-info">
  <strong>Coming Soon</strong> — The [% entity_name | html %] section is currently under development and will be available shortly.
</div>

[% IF entity_desc %]
<p>[% entity_desc | html %]</p>
[% END %]

[% IF is_admin && add_url %]
<p>
  <a href="[% add_url | html %]" class="btn btn-primary">Add [% entity_name | html %]</a>
</p>
[% END %]

<p>In the meantime, you can use the <strong>Ask AI</strong> feature to look up information:</p>
<div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;max-width:520px;margin:1rem 0;">
  <input type="text" id="cs-ai-query" placeholder="Ask about a [% entity_name.lower | html %]..." style="flex:1;padding:0.4rem 0.7rem;border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:4px;font-size:var(--font-size-small);background:var(--secondary-color);color:var(--text-color);" />
  <button onclick="csAskAI()" style="padding:0.4rem 1rem;background:var(--info-color);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;">Ask AI</button>
</div>
<script>
function csAskAI() {
    var q = document.getElementById('cs-ai-query').value.trim();
    if (!q) return;
    window.open('/AI/chat?prompt=' + encodeURIComponent('Tell me about this [% entity_name | html %] in the context of natural health and biological medicine: ' + q), '_blank');
}
document.getElementById('cs-ai-query').addEventListener('keypress', function(e) { if (e.key === 'Enter') csAskAI(); });
</script>
